Mission Orders

Troops are unable to safely move through the jungle for fear of being attacked.

Get in there and kill the {@LinkCreature:10#11#naga slayers}, {@LinkCreature:10#12#caiman serfs}, {@LinkCreature:10#5#thickbark ghilliedhus}, {@LinkCreature:10#6#agitated mycanars}, and {@LinkCreature:10#21#ebon sabertooths}.

Report to Coordinator Briale when mission is complete.
You've earned the thanks of the federation. Your guild is an inspiration to all!
